00:57:00.104 --> 00:57:02.231 line:90% position:50% align:center
Our postcard this month takes us

00:57:02.231 --> 00:57:04.942 line:90% position:50% align:center
to the beautiful country of Paraguay.

00:57:04.942 --> 00:57:09.697 line:90% position:50% align:center
Paraguay is a landlocked country
in the heart of South America,

00:57:09.697 --> 00:57:12.700 line:90% position:50% align:center
with a population of about seven million.

00:57:13.450 --> 00:57:17.579 line:90% position:50% align:center
The Paraguay River runs
from north to south, dividing the country.

00:57:18.580 --> 00:57:23.043 line:90% position:50% align:center
The east is characterized
by rolling hills and fertile fields

00:57:23.043 --> 00:57:25.504 line:90% position:50% align:center
—some of which have red soil

00:57:25.504 --> 00:57:27.715 line:90% position:50% align:center
and thick forests.

00:57:27.715 --> 00:57:32.261 line:90% position:50% align:center
In contrast,
the western region has a sparse population,

00:57:32.261 --> 00:57:35.306 line:90% position:50% align:center
coarse grass, scrub forests,

00:57:35.306 --> 00:57:37.141 line:90% position:50% align:center
vast swamps,

00:57:37.141 --> 00:57:40.602 line:90% position:50% align:center
and diverse colorful tropical birds.

00:57:41.228 --> 00:57:43.689 line:90% position:50% align:center
Paraguay has two official languages:

00:57:43.689 --> 00:57:46.358 line:90% position:50% align:center
Spanish and Guaraní.

00:57:46.358 --> 00:57:48.694 line:90% position:50% align:center
And when the two languages mix,

00:57:48.694 --> 00:57:50.863 line:90% position:50% align:center
you get Jopara,

00:57:50.863 --> 00:57:53.073 line:90% position:50% align:center
which is frequently used today.

00:57:53.949 --> 00:57:56.285 line:90% position:50% align:center
Paraguay’s theocratic history began

00:57:56.285 --> 00:57:59.747 line:90% position:50% align:center
when Eberhard Hoeckle,
a German immigrant,

00:57:59.747 --> 00:58:04.752 line:90% position:50% align:center
found a tract randomly sent
to his home from world headquarters.

00:58:04.752 --> 00:58:08.380 line:90% position:50% align:center
This moved him to order
<i>Studies in the Scriptures.</i>

00:58:08.380 --> 00:58:10.382 line:90% position:50% align:center
In 1906,

00:58:10.382 --> 00:58:13.469 line:90% position:50% align:center
he and his brother-in-law
baptized each other,

00:58:13.469 --> 00:58:17.473 line:90% position:50% align:center
becoming the first in Paraguay
to accept Bible truth.

00:58:18.307 --> 00:58:20.309 line:90% position:50% align:center
In 1924,

00:58:20.309 --> 00:58:24.188 line:90% position:50% align:center
Juan Muñiz,
a faithful missionary from Spain,

00:58:24.188 --> 00:58:26.815 line:90% position:50% align:center
arrived to spread the Kingdom message

00:58:26.815 --> 00:58:29.651 line:90% position:50% align:center
throughout several South American countries,

00:58:29.651 --> 00:58:31.653 line:90% position:50% align:center
including Paraguay.

00:58:32.529 --> 00:58:34.615 line:90% position:50% align:center
Then in 1934,

00:58:34.615 --> 00:58:39.119 line:90% position:50% align:center
Brothers Martonfi, Koros, and Rebacz

00:58:39.119 --> 00:58:43.791 line:90% position:50% align:center
entered the country
despite the ongoing Chaco War.

00:58:43.791 --> 00:58:45.793 line:90% position:50% align:center
Their efforts paid off

00:58:45.793 --> 00:58:49.797 line:90% position:50% align:center
when the first congregation
was formed five years later.

00:58:50.714 --> 00:58:54.968 line:90% position:50% align:center
Decades of political instability
resulted in a decree

00:58:54.968 --> 00:58:59.765 line:90% position:50% align:center
revoking the organization’s
legal status in 1979.

00:59:00.849 --> 00:59:04.061 line:90% position:50% align:center
As a result,
the brothers had to conduct meetings

00:59:04.061 --> 00:59:07.106 line:90% position:50% align:center
in small groups at private homes

00:59:07.106 --> 00:59:09.691 line:90% position:50% align:center
or in isolated areas.

00:59:09.691 --> 00:59:13.904 line:90% position:50% align:center
Fortunately, 12 years later, in 1991,

00:59:13.904 --> 00:59:17.116 line:90% position:50% align:center
the organization was legally recognized

00:59:17.116 --> 00:59:20.536 line:90% position:50% align:center
after the fall of the military regime.

00:59:20.536 --> 00:59:23.497 line:90% position:50% align:center
Did the publishers
dwindle during those years?

00:59:23.497 --> 00:59:25.040 line:90% position:50% align:center
Hardly!

00:59:25.040 --> 00:59:28.168 line:90% position:50% align:center
The number of publishers doubled in size.

00:59:28.168 --> 00:59:32.131 line:90% position:50% align:center
Today, there are over 11,000 publishers

00:59:32.131 --> 00:59:35.300 line:90% position:50% align:center
who conduct about 10,000 Bible studies

00:59:35.300 --> 00:59:38.929 line:90% position:50% align:center
and attend 183 congregations.

00:59:40.097 --> 00:59:42.099 line:90% position:50% align:center
In the western part of the country,

00:59:42.099 --> 00:59:44.476 line:90% position:50% align:center
we find the Filadelfia Español

00:59:44.476 --> 00:59:48.230 line:90% position:50% align:center
and Loma Plata Guaraní Congregations.

00:59:48.230 --> 00:59:52.276 line:90% position:50% align:center
The 95 publishers of these two congregations

00:59:52.276 --> 00:59:56.488 line:90% position:50% align:center
conduct an average of 155 Bible studies

00:59:56.488 --> 00:59:58.323 line:90% position:50% align:center
and preach in Spanish,

00:59:58.323 --> 01:00:01.368 line:90% position:50% align:center
Guaraní, Low German,

01:00:01.368 --> 01:00:03.203 line:90% position:50% align:center
and Nivaclé.

01:00:03.996 --> 01:00:06.081 line:90% position:50% align:center
The Filadelfia Español

01:00:06.081 --> 01:00:10.294 line:90% position:50% align:center
and Loma Plata Guaraní Congregations
send their love.

01:00:11.003 --> 01:00:14.256 line:90% position:50% align:center
We love you all very much.

